.com/immeme0/status/2051001915530498248", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Shocking video shows a landlord revealing how his Section 8 tenant left the property after eviction, alongside another tenant who was paying cash.", "last_comment_created": 1778087127268, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 9, "score_up": 32, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 894, "created": 1777831937000, "id": "2051001915530498248", "video": {"preview": "https://pbs.twimg.com/amplify_video_thumb/2051001839974240256/img/WqxAKpWIgUBIfErZ.jpg", "mpeg": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2051001839974240256/pl/aExBHkcHJ3tRbcV8.m3u8?v=512", "aspectRatio": [9, 16], "heightRatio": 177, "type": "video/mp4", "url": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2051001839974240256/vid/avc1/320x568/fiROCZV2rtQgP-Ci.mp4"}, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1511105748671021065/h4NfG141_normal.jpg", "displayName": "I Meme Therefore I Am \ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8", "username": "ImMeme0"}, "content": "Shocking video shows a landlord revealing how his Section 8 tenant left the property after eviction, alongside another tenant who was paying cash.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 18955}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsL4AnyS", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 81, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "hat", "id": 8602258, "raw_content": "You got buildings in Ohio right now that look completely empty... but somehow they're sucking up **MILLIONS** in Medicaid money like a black hole. Ghost companies. Fraud everywhere. Taxpayers getting bilked while honest Ohio families pay the price. This is a giant scam that's been running for years.\n\nVivek Ramaswamy just laid it all out, a super simple plan:\n\n1. **Stop the Bleeding First**  \n   There are already laws on the books. Use them to go after the big fraud cases HARD. Prosecute the scammers so they feel it. Send a clear message: \"You steal from Ohio taxpayers, you pay the price.\" Not complicated. Just spine and action.\n\n2. **Fix the Broken Game**  \n   Right now, if a state like Ohio actually saves money by cutting fraud, the feds punish them by sending LESS money back. It's backwards! Here's the fix: Change the rules so states that clean house get to KEEP more of the savings. Reward smart government like you reward a good business.\n\n3. **End the Dependency Trap**  \n   When people stay on welfare forever, no job, no purpose... it kills their soul. Depression, anxiety, feeling worthless. Vivek gets it: Handouts feel nice short term but destroy lives long term. Real help means giving people **agency** \u2013 the power to stand on their own feet.\n\n4. **Make Ohio Thunder Again**  \n   Take the money saved from fraud \u2192 Slash property taxes, income taxes, make the state attractive for real high-paying jobs. Kids graduate high school or college and actually get good work instead of signing up for SNAP. Factories humming and Families strong. No more purposelessness.\n\nNo grievance nonsense. No socialist crap. Just cut waste, fire the lazy bureaucrats who won't do their jobs, reward results, and revive the spirit that made America great.\n\nSAVE OHIO.\n\nYou can watch him detail the plan here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YMXQjWxVQTw", "author": "ShiningShrine", "created": 1778064417278, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Bastard", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "VIVEK RAMASWAMY JUST DROPPED THE ULTIMATE RED PILL FOR OHIO \u2013 NO MORE FREE MONEY SCAMS, REAL JOBS & AMERICAN DREAM BACK ON! (MUST READ)", "last_comment_created": 1778080197698, "content": "<p>You got buildings in Ohio right now that look completely empty... but somehow they're sucking up <strong>MILLIONS</strong> in Medicaid money like a black hole. Ghost companies. Fraud everywhere. Taxpayers getting bilked while honest Ohio families pay the price. This is a giant scam that's been running for years.</p>\n<p>Vivek Ramaswamy just laid it all out, a super simple plan:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Stop the Bleeding First</strong><br />\nThere are already laws on the books. Use them to go after the big fraud cases HARD. Prosecute the scammers so they feel it. Send a clear message: &quot;You steal from Ohio taxpayers, you pay the price.&quot; Not complicated. Just spine and action.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Fix the Broken Game</strong><br />\nRight now, if a state like Ohio actually saves money by cutting fraud, the feds punish them by sending LESS money back. It's backwards! Here's the fix: Change the rules so states that clean house get to KEEP more of the savings. Reward smart government like you reward a good business.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>End the Dependency Trap</strong><br />\nWhen people stay on welfare forever, no job, no purpose... it kills their soul. Depression, anxiety, feeling worthless. Vivek gets it: Handouts feel nice short term but destroy lives long term. Real help means giving people <strong>agency</strong> \u2013 the power to stand on their own feet.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Make Ohio Thunder Again</strong><br />\nTake the money saved from fraud \u2192 Slash property taxes, income taxes, make the state attractive for real high-paying jobs. Kids graduate high school or college and actually get good work instead of signing up for SNAP. Factories humming and Families strong. No more purposelessness.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>No grievance nonsense. No socialist crap. Just cut waste, fire the lazy bureaucrats who won't do their jobs, reward results, and revive the spirit that made America great.</p>\n<p>SAVE OHIO.</p>\n<p>You can watch him detail the plan here: <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YMXQjWxVQTw\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YMXQjWxVQTw</a></p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 22, "score_up": 81, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "SAVE AMERICA", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsL4BM4T", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 55, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8602455, "raw_content": "", "author": "Eruditio", "created": 1778071894899, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Andy_Man45", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "justthenews.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsL4BM4T.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://justthenews.com/politics-policy/gun-rights/wedtop-doj-official-predicts-supreme-court-will-declare-ar-15-rifles", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": " Top DOJ official predicts Supreme Court will declare AR-15 rifles legal everywhere in America.\n\n\"I think there is going to be a ruling eventually from the Supreme Court that AR-15s are legal for all law-abiding citizens to own and operate,\" Assist